Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:11.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,滚啊滚 滚啊滚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 咱们可不是堆雪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:20.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么滚雪会运得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到居然会遇险被困在雪山里 还在这里搭起了冰屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是在说笑话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得他好激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:34.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 贵志跟健吾现在都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们四个人得一起做点事才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那遇险到底有什么危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,危险的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我们现在没东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,健吾 贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,遇险可真是相当危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:56.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:02.20,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:09.30,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の面影思い出す　ふとした時に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:30.38,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:36.11,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.91,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.72,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.53,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.89,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.66,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:59.09,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:05.34,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.15,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:14.64,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:02.20,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:09.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:30.38,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在记忆之中 你微笑着的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:36.11,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡无奇的日常 是无可替的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.91,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}这份思念之情 现在终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.72,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你欢笑度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.53,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你争论泪流的曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.89,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们携手的每一天 令人无比怜爱的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.66,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:59.09,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:05.34,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回忆起你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.15,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遥遥可见的那条街道的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:14.64,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露着笑容吗
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们就在这里等待救援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:33.71,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(960,960)\an8\3c&HFFFFFF&}第十二话 雪祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还得尽量保存体能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然比较艰难 但大家一定要坚持住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像会很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:44.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说 我可以一直这样近距离地待在三岛旁边了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺不赖的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上这么冷的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:52.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了 抱歉我太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:59.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 要是他们还是不来救我们的话会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:00.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上个厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 把气氛搞得一团糟就开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我说这条是近路才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是健吾的错啦 这是大家的决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:27.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这是大家判断的失误啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:33.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这事不赖我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这反应真讨打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 雏是不是有点慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 别吓我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:04.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:10.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是救援的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在哪里看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:19.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经出现幻象了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 有件事我希望你们替我保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我能使用超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我飞上天去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这回又变成妄想了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:54.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三岛 再怎么说也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这样奖励她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 快醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在只能等待救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:11.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在山里乱逛平白消耗体力的话 你可能会死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:16.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不阻止她的话 小雏她会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:28.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会使用超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是我们产生幻觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们是什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏从厕所回来之后 事情就变得不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:52.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道她去了厕所就一直没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我飘起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:10.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 雏你还真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经还以为你就是台造粪机器的 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就用小雏的能力去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饿 能力用不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那刚才的事情算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,健吾跟贵志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他们了 你现在能用超能力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 用不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你跟我来一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 这之后你可以闭上眼睛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼就有饭吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在雪山里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临雪山寿司店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 你就坐这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:26.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 你要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鲑鱼子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,客人您还真是幸运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的话 还能吃新鲜的鱼子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 鲑鱼子军舰寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:45.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:51.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好凉啊 这是雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,客人你不要说傻话啊 这就是鲑鱼子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是还没完全解冻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 再多来点鲑鱼子军舰寿司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏你看 真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:23.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你多吃点肚子就饱了 也就可以用能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:29.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:30.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是山葵太辣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:42.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说鲑鱼子里是不放山葵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你快看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看她吃得多香…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 我看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧雏 想吃多少都有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:50.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,仅限鲑鱼子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：「想吃多少」和「鲑鱼子」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉只要努力一下 就可以使用能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:14.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:21.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿 我们在这儿 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:27.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 在这儿会有雪祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:35.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在扮醋姜片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别管这个了 赶快营救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:48.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这孩子真是的 老是让我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:02.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃真正的鲑鱼子 要解冻后的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能平安健康地活着我就知足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去刷盘子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,旅游开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 下次杏子你也跟我们去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\blur2\3c&H28A994&\c&H030053&\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H171717&\pos(390,348)}特集 当代黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正姚体\fs50\pos(410,414)\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H0D0C16&}渴求{\c&H393CB7&\3c&HFFFFFF&}血{\c&H171717&}与暴力与金钱的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1526,534)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}Q你们之间没有人情世故吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是休息日 但也别睡到中午啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\fs80\fn思源宋体 CN\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}然后三年后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里 真是漫长的旅途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和小雏相遇后过了快三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会找到能让我们的摇滚幻觉秀完成的线索的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:17.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聚在这里的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:21.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来请大家观赏超人拳法的气功精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望入门的请到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是我梦寐以求的幻觉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像小雏那样的不可思议力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:50.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不来学习就不能和她说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了 我听不懂中文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停 暂停 my name is 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:04.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人 请不要和无关人员牵扯过多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好 my name is 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为真绪大人您是超人拳法的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}等… I am 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:10.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,I am rocker！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里包衣食住 我本以为会很轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总觉得变得越来越奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:28.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 汉服最开始是觉得挺可爱的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直穿一样的也腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小雏 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能穿就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:36.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就快三年了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样都想去日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:09.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来刚才那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:19.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人今天也跟木头人用日语在碎碎念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟往常一样啊 真是古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:29.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 听说白天的演武有日本人混进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一 要对他加紧监视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:38.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的超人拳法 是不可以失去那个孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 小雏 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是打碎壶的那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 I am 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 接下来的话用中文怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是昨天那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 摇滚的话是世界共同的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话只要唱歌就行了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用唱也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 日语？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的乐队「CENTRAL PARK」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是对摇滚加以幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开拓了摇滚幻觉秀这一全新音乐种类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们去了美国学习幻觉把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:20.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那里进行的 只是魔术而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那时 我看到了你的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得「就是这个！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就想着说 我所追求的真正的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是可以用气功再现啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相当古怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:40.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想知道日本的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可能不要跟这个人说太多话比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人也觉得是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女孩子不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在跟自己制作的人偶说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪到这个地步 气功就无法变厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还真摇滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我接下来还有事 就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:01.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让小雏看看 没有她我们也能做到那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请教我气功!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说「小雏」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏是指这孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 大概是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,发色之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:24.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于… 终于有线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我来教你气功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换 请带我去见小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们现在都还是邮件好友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人 差不多到要回去的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:47.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我还有点话想跟这个人说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 好不容易抓到了小雏的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样被光头佬带回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能就再也没有机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:01.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:03.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,追!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:06.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 为什么要逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,各种原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人 你居然攻击同门师兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全员一起上 把她抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的超能力伪装出来的冒牌拳法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是被称为内家拳的顶点的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手机啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是没打电话的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 把他们都打飞就会暴露我的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样的话我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:22.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:26.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被抬手抓着而已我就浮起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉是！跟小雏的幻觉把戏相同!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是在追求这个啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:46.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:47.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说把这个皱巴巴又光溜溜的老光头扔出去就糟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别犯傻了 说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:09.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了师傅慧眼挖掘出了你的才能还有养育之恩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:12.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用官员的关系 还为身位孤儿的你做了个身份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:16.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用我的力量增加门徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:19.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,收到的学费应该也不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:22.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我已经偿还恩义了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无妨 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在电视上被介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在全国各地建立了十个分部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这全都是真绪你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:41.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 如果你能出色地完成超人拳法的试炼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就认可你去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 难道说要把那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个至今为止都没人成功过啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:48.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:48.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:49.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没人成功过 难道说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:50.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太危险了啊！师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}无妨…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:00.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:07.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪 将这个铁人利落地破坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:14.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪啊 无人怀疑你的内家拳功力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:23.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 对着这个铁人只允许用外家拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 稍微再修行一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后再去日本 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要上吗 开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:35.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 再怎么说那个也摇滚过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:36.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把如此高速旋转的铁棒停下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:26.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪啊 我就允许你去日本建立分部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不论什么手段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要大量地拉拢客人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就是头号弟子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你 我应该不用困扰在日本怎么生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:52.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于 终于要迈上摇滚幻觉秀的道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:57.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于 终于能跟斑鸠说我的球不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:02.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:06.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去往小雏和杏子在等待着的 日本
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:29.14,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}毎日が穏やかに過ぎてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:34.73,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}同じ日々を繰り返して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:41.70,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}なんとなく過ごしているのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:47.21,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}一緒に探そう　輝く未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:54.34,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}知らないことがたくさんで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:58.29,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}クラクラしっちゃて　あっがちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:04.99,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}生まれて初めてのキモチ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.26,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}大好きこころは無重力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.97,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}だんだん体をふわり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.44,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}太陽まで届きそうなぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.95,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}不思議だね　キモチ一つで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:27.24,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}こんなに見える世界が ぐっと見えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:34.01,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}新しい一日が回り出すよ
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:29.14,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}每一天都安稳地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:34.73,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}重复着平淡无奇的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:41.70,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}日子不知不觉就过去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:47.21,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}一起去寻找吧 那光辉的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:54.34,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}未知的事情堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:58.29,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}昏头转向  心情激动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:04.99,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}人生第一次体验到的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.26,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}最喜欢的心情没有重力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.97,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}身体慢慢变得轻飘飘了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.44,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}好像快要飞到太阳上一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.95,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}这一份心情 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:27.24,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}没想到世界变得如此清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:34.01,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}来开始新的一天吧
